{"tid":1828772,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有團體反對香港電台　港台稱有既定機制處理投訴","createTime":"2020-01-18T06:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T07:40:39.000Z","uid":89591,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"690857e1e2065f59cde7922ab74c025421bbb39b","tid":1828772,"uid":89591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T06:46:14.000Z","msg":"食撚屎啦五毛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n/有團體發起包圍香港電台行動，集會人士手持大型國旗和標語，在港台對出的廣播道行人路集會，並高叫「支持香港警察」、「反對香港電台」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n港台機構傳訊組總監伍曼儀接收團體投訴信，她表示港台有既定機制處理投訴。對於示威人士要求開放大氣電波，伍曼儀說，有關人士可參與「社區廣播計劃」。<br />\n<br />\n集會期間，財政司司長陳茂波正在港台出席《眾言堂》節目，由於節目完結時，示威人士仍在港台正門聚集，陳茂波乘坐的車輛要由另一個閘口離開。/<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503507-20200118.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503507-20200118.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=601bed5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503507-20200118.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a37de52e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503507-20200118.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"196d1793cbf733bf4ea3c9588d15da52f572c89e","tid":1828772,"uid":59633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:40:39.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}